Marisa Henry

Hi there!

My name is Marisa. Im a data scientist, currently based in Montreal.

My work is focused on the design and evaluation of data-driven programs, technologies, and systems to improve societal well-being. I have proven experience tackling complex analyses and communicating actionable insights from these analyses through presentations, written reports, and data visualizations.

Outside of work, I love hiking, playing with my dog, and exploring various creative outlets.

If youre interested in collaborating, please reach out! :)

Education

Cambridge University | MPhil Engineering for Sustainable Development, Gates Cambridge Scholar

Purdue University | BS Environmental and Ecological Engineering

Experience

Transit | Data Scientist | September 2021 - Present

Stantec | Data Engineer & Scientist | January 2021 - August 2021

Mathematica Policy Research | Data Scientist | July 2019 - January 2021
